  <brief_title>Typical Flutter Ablation:A Comparison of 4 mm Versus 2 mm Irrigated cathéters</brief_title>
  <official_title>Typical Flutter Ablation:A Comparison of 4 mm Versus 2 mm Irrigated cathéters</official_title>
