  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The purpose of this study is to compare the efficacy of 4 mm irrigated catheters with 2 mm
      irrigated catheters for ablation of typical flutter.It's a prospective randomised multicenter
      study.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
