  <eligibility>
    <criteria>
      <textblock>
        Inclusion Criteria:

          -  All patients above the age 18 years undergoing a first catheter ablation for typical
             atrial flutter

        Exclusion Criteria:

          -  Pregnancy

          -  Hemodynamic instability

          -  A recurrence of previous ablated typical atrial flutter
      </textblock>
